heading: Darien (Panama and Colombia).
general-note: Here are entered works on the region of Spanish colonial territory comprising at its greatest extent the easternmost part of the Isthmus of Panama and the eastern side of Urabá Gulf in the departments of Antioquia and Chocó of Colombia. Works on the present Panamanian province of Darien are entered under the name heading. Darien (Panama : Province)..
